This is an example implementation utilizing Facebook Graph API implemented on Chrome WebApp.
Before you try this out, you need to change a few lines of code as well as setting up a Facebook App.
You can create Facebook App from following page.
http://developers.facebook.com/setup

============
Prerequisite
============
You must have following:
- Chrome Browser
- Facebook Account
- Facebook App
- Web server you can place "server/callback.html"

====================
Edit following files
====================
1. crx/index.html
Around line 23, change "api_key" and "callback_url" params.
"api_key" should be provided by Facebook if you own an Facebook App.
"callback_url" must be the same url you have set on your Facebook App. Also, you have to be able to place server/callback.html on exact same url.

2. server/callback.html
